Class ScriptEngineManagerImpl

  • java.lang.Object

      • uk.co.strangeskies.scripting.impl.ScriptEngineManagerImpl

  • public class ScriptEngineManagerImpl
extends javax.script.ScriptEngineManager
    An implementation of ScriptEngineManager for the OSGi environment. Services registered for ScriptEngineFactory will be registered automatically.
